---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const standards = [
  { num: '01', title: 'A real provider reads your chart', body: 'I review and approve every protocol myself. No questionnaire quietly handing out prescriptions while a clinician rubber-stamps the queue.' },
  { num: '02', title: 'FDA-regulated 503A pharmacies', body: 'Your compounded medication comes from sterile pharmacies that do third-party testing for potency and sterility. No grey-market peptides, ever.' },
  { num: '03', title: 'You can actually reach me', body: 'Message me directly. Follow-ups are built in, scheduling is a priority, and you will never sit on hold with a call center.' },
  { num: '04', title: 'You know what you pay', body: 'One flat monthly membership covers it: your medication, supplies, home delivery, follow-ups. Nothing gets sprung on you later.' },
];
---

<Layout
  title="About Liliana Damron, APRN, FNP-BC | Founder | Viva Wellness Co."
  description="Liliana Damron, APRN, FNP-BC, founded Viva Wellness Co. to deliver concierge peptide therapy, hormone optimization, and GLP-1 weight loss via telehealth. Background in geriatric medicine. Practicing in Austin, TX, Colorado, Florida, and Iowa."
  schema={{
    '@context': 'https://schema.org',
    '@graph': [
      {
        '@type': 'Person',
        '@id': 'https://vivawellnessco.com/about#liliana',
        name: 'Liliana Damron',
        honorificSuffix: 'APRN, FNP-BC',
        jobTitle: 'Family Nurse Practitioner, Founder',
        description: 'Founder and lead provider of Viva Wellness Co., a concierge telehealth practice delivering peptide therapy, hormone optimization, and GLP-1 weight loss from Austin, Texas.',
        worksFor: { '@id': 'https://vivawellnessco.com/#organization' },
        image: 'https://vivawellnessco.com/liliana.webp',
        url: 'https://vivawellnessco.com/about',
        knowsAbout: ['Peptide Therapy', 'Hormone Replacement Therapy', 'GLP-1 Weight Loss', 'Performance Medicine', 'Geriatric Medicine'],
      },
      {
        '@type': 'BreadcrumbList',
        itemListElement: [
          { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 1, name: 'Home', item: 'https://vivawellnessco.com/' },
          { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 2, name: 'Provider', item: 'https://vivawellnessco.com/about' },
        ],
      },
    ],
  }}
>

  {/* HERO */}
  <section class="about-hero">
    <img class="about-hero__bg" src="/about-hero.webp" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="eager" decoding="async" />
    <div class="container about-hero__inner">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal" style="--d: 100ms;">· The provider</span>
      <h1 class="about-hero__title">
        <span class="reveal" style="--d: 200ms;">Meet your</span><br/>
        <span class="italic-display reveal" style="--d: 360ms;">provider.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="lead reveal" style="--d: 700ms;">
        I'm Liliana Damron, APRN, FNP-BC, and I started Viva to do the opposite
        of what I watched every day in geriatric medicine. Catch the trouble
        early. Keep people strong and able longer. Make healthspan match
        lifespan. Your first visit is with me, not a delegate.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* FOUNDER */}
  <section class="section section--paper">
    <div class="container founder">
      <div class="founder__media">
        <div class="founder__frame" transition:name="provider-photo">
          <img src="/liliana-new.webp" alt="Liliana Damron, APRN, FNP-BC" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="founder__caption">
          <div>Liliana Damron</div>
          <div class="founder__creds">APRN, FNP-BC · Founder</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="founder__copy">
        <span class="index" data-num="01">The founder</span>
        <h2 class="founder__title">
          I watched <span class="italic-display">preventable disease</span> take people's lives apart. So I started doing the opposite.
        </h2>
        <p class="lead">
          I spent my early career caring for people whose bodies had stopped
          working. Strength gone. Independence gone. The quality of their days
          worn down by metabolic dysfunction and chronic disease that had been
          decades in the making.
        </p>
        <p>
          Most of it was preventable. Not all of it, but most. After a while you
          can't stop seeing the pattern: insulin resistance, hormones slipping,
          muscle wasting, inflammation, the slow grind of small things nobody
          looked at. By the time someone landed in my clinic, the window to
          prevent any of it had closed twenty years earlier.
        </p>
        <p>
          That's why Viva exists. Catch the trouble early. Build strength on
          purpose. Treat your body the way a serious athlete treats training,
          with real numbers, a clear plan, and adjustments as you go. What I'm
          after is more of the years where you still feel like yourself, so your
          healthspan finally catches up to your lifespan.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* MARQUEE */}
  <div class="marquee" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="marquee-track">
      <span>Function over decline</span>
      <span>Prevention over rescue</span>
      <span>Measurement over guessing</span>
      <span>Performance over maintenance</span>
      <span>Function over decline</span>
      <span>Prevention over rescue</span>
      <span>Measurement over guessing</span>
      <span>Performance over maintenance</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  {/* STANDARDS */}
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="index" data-num="02">The standards</span>
        <h2 class="section-head__title">
          What concierge <span class="italic-display">actually</span> means here.
        </h2>
        <p class="lead section-head__lead">
          A lot of telehealth brands sell the cheapest version of medicine the
          law will let them. I built Viva on the opposite bet. Here's what that
          looks like in practice.
        </p>
      </div>

      <ol class="standards">
        {standards.map((s) => (
          <li class="standard">
            <span class="standard__num">{s.num}</span>
            <div class="standard__content">
              <h3 class="standard__title">{s.title}</h3>
              <p class="standard__body">{s.body}</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* SERVICE AREA */}
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container service-area">
      <div>
        <span class="index" data-num="03">The reach</span>
        <h2 class="service-area__title">
          Licensed where you <span class="italic-display">already are.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="lead">
          Viva is 100% telehealth. We meet by secure video, your medications and
          supplies come to your door, and follow-ups happen by message or video.
          No commute, no waiting room, no parking garage.
        </p>
        <p>
          I am currently licensed to see patients in Texas, Colorado, Florida,
          and Iowa, and I add new states regularly. If yours isn't on the list,
          tell me. It honestly helps me decide where to go next.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="states">
        <div class="state state--active">
          <div class="state__abbrev">TX</div>
          <div class="state__name">Texas</div>
          <div class="state__status">Active</div>
        </div>
        <div class="state state--active">
          <div class="state__abbrev">CO</div>
          <div class="state__name">Colorado</div>
          <div class="state__status">Active</div>
        </div>
        <div class="state state--active">
          <div class="state__abbrev">FL</div>
          <div class="state__name">Florida</div>
          <div class="state__status">Active</div>
        </div>
        <div class="state state--active">
          <div class="state__abbrev">IA</div>
          <div class="state__name">Iowa</div>
          <div class="state__status">Active</div>
        </div>
        <form class="state state--add" id="state-form" novalidate>
          <div class="state__abbrev">+</div>
          <input class="state__input" name="state" placeholder="Your state" maxlength="24" autocomplete="address-level1" required aria-label="Tell me your state" />
          <button class="state__add-btn" type="submit">Tell me</button>
        </form>
        <div class="state state--active state--thanks" id="state-thanks" hidden>
          <div class="state__abbrev">&#10003;</div>
          <div class="state__name">Thank you</div>
          <div class="state__status" id="state-thanks-status">Noted</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* CTA */}
  <section class="about-cta">
    <div class="container about-cta__inner">
      <h2 class="about-cta__title">
        The protocol starts with <span class="italic-display">one visit.</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="about-cta__ctas">
        <a href="/start?utm_source=vivawellnessco&utm_medium=cta&utm_content=about_cta" class="btn btn--bronze">Book your first visit</a>
        <a href="/#quiz" class="btn">Find your protocol</a>
        <a href="/services" class="btn">See programs</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* HERO */
  .about-hero {
    padding: clamp(6rem, 12vw, 10rem) 0 clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .about-hero__bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; z-index: 0; opacity: 0.4; }
  .about-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 1;
    background: radial-gradient(900px 500px at 75% 0%, rgba(201, 120, 58, 0.18), transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .about-hero::after { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 1; background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(20,13,9,0.5), rgba(20,13,9,0.72)); pointer-events: none; }
  .about-hero__inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 1100px;
  }
  .about-hero__title {
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6.8vw, 5.4rem);
    line-height: 1.02;
    letter-spacing: -0.028em;
    max-width: 14ch;
  }

  /* FOUNDER */
  .founder {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 5fr 7fr;
    gap: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 6rem);
    align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .founder { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .founder__media {
    position: sticky;
    top: 100px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.2rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .founder__media { position: static; } }
  .founder__frame {
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bronze-deep) 0%, var(--ink-3) 100%);
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .founder__frame img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
    display: block;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .founder__frame::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 100 100' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.6' numOctaves='2'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='0.4'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    mix-blend-mode: overlay;
  }
  .founder__mono {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(8rem, 16vw, 16rem);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--paper);
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144, 'SOFT' 70;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .founder__caption {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .founder__creds {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--bronze-deep);
    margin-top: 0.4rem;
  }
  .founder__title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.8vw, 3.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    max-width: 20ch;
  }
  .founder__title .italic-display { color: var(--bronze-deep); }
  .founder__copy p { margin-bottom: 1.3rem; max-width: 62ch; }

  /* STANDARDS */
  .standards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule-strong);
  }
  .standard {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr;
    gap: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 4rem);
    padding: 2.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .standard__num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--bronze);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    padding-top: 0.5rem;
  }
  .standard__title {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2.8vw, 2.4rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .standard__body {
    color: rgba(245, 241, 234, 0.7);
    max-width: 60ch;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .standard { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 0.8rem; padding: 2rem 0; }
  }

  /* SERVICE AREA */
  .service-area {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 6fr 5fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .service-area { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .service-area__title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3.4rem);
    margin: 1rem 0 1.2rem;
    max-width: 18ch;
  }
  .service-area__title .italic-display { color: var(--bronze); }
  .service-area p { margin-bottom: 1.2rem; max-width: 56ch; }
  .states {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--rule-strong);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule-strong);
  }
  .state[hidden] { display: none; }
  .state {
    background: var(--ink);
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    transition: background 220ms var(--ease);
  }
  .state__abbrev {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 360;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--paper);
  }
  .state--active .state__abbrev { color: var(--bronze); }
  .state__name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--paper);
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
  }
  .state__status {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mute);
  }
  .state--active .state__status { color: var(--bronze); }
  .state__input {
    background: transparent;
    border: 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule-strong);
    color: var(--paper);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    padding: 0.35rem 0;
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
    transition: border-color 200ms var(--ease);
  }
  .state__input::placeholder { color: var(--mute); }
  .state__input:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--bronze); }
  .state__add-btn {
    margin-top: 0.7rem;
    align-self: flex-start;
    background: transparent;
    border: 0;
    color: var(--bronze);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0;
    transition: color 200ms var(--ease);
  }
  .state__add-btn:hover { color: var(--bronze-bright); }

  /* CTA */
  .about-cta {
    padding: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 9rem) 0;
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--ink);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .about-cta::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(700px 400px at 50% 0%, rgba(201, 120, 58, 0.18), transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .about-cta__inner { position: relative; }
  .about-cta__title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 18ch;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  .about-cta__title .italic-display { color: var(--bronze-bright); }
  .about-cta__ctas { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
</style>

<script>
  const f = document.getElementById('state-form');
  if (f) {
    f.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
      e.preventDefault();
      const input = f.querySelector('input[name="state"]');
      const v = (input && input.value ? input.value : '').trim();
      if (!v) { if (input) input.focus(); return; }
      const thanks = document.getElementById('state-thanks');
      const status = document.getElementById('state-thanks-status');
      if (status) status.textContent = 'Noted · ' + v;
      f.setAttribute('hidden', '');
      if (thanks) thanks.removeAttribute('hidden');
    });
  }
</script>
